quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,"Nditsuba khu tini nende zaituni!"
  95,2,"Nende khulukulu lwa Sinai!"
  95,3,"Nende khulitokho lino liomulembe po!"
  95,4,"Khubwatoto khwaloonga Omundu okhuloonga okhulayi muno."
  95,5,"Mana nikhumukalusia hasi muno okhushila abali hasi!"
  95,6,"Halali balia Abasuubila mana nibakhola amalayi. Abo balinyoola omurungo kulawa tawe."
  95,7,"Mana nishina nikhwakhamala shilakhukhola okhukatsula inyanga yomurungo?"
  95,8,"Nyasaye shali niye wukhalakanga eshiina obulai muno okhushila abakhalakanga eshina boosi?"
